'''Katie Cook''' is an artist whose art is featured in the [[Star Wars: 30th Anniversary Collection|''Star Wars: 30th Anniversary'']] and the "[[Star Wars: Galaxy 4]]" Trading Card Sets. She was one of the four artists who worked on [[Star Wars: The Clone Wars (webcomics)|''The Clone Wars'' web comics]].

